snippet.title: John Davis True Crime
snippet.description: You could help Solve a Mystery !  I welcome all to my channel and hope you will share your thoughts with me. I love a good mystery ! Dont you ? Leave a Comment if you have a mystery you would like me to tackle ! Know of a case that hasnt gotten much attention ? leave me the details and I will help spread the message. Like to talk politics and want to hear my take just ask!
